Netdata Github wiki:  https://github.com/firehol/netdata/wiki/Installation#linux-one-liner

1. Installation
Linux one liner
For all Linux systems, you can use this one liner to install the git version of netdata:
# basic netdata installation
bash <(curl -Ss https://my-netdata.io/kickstart.sh)

# or

# install required packages for all netdata plugins
bash <(curl -Ss https://my-netdata.io/kickstart.sh) all

========================================================================================
After Linux one liner basic netdata isntallation, I got some output like:


